entries.femaleVariant: I know what you're thinkin' – why's my crazy output leaving a message on the machine while I'm making breakfast?

So, uh – ahem – what the hell, I figured I'd just tell you here.
V, I just wanted you to know that... I'm happy. For the first time in my life. And I wanted to--
Rise and shine! Breakfast on the table!
Speak o' the devil... See you soon. Mwah!
